### 1.7 Display Pipeline
EDID handshake, KMS mode set, framebuffer commitment. No visual state without hardware validation.

### 1.8 Determinism Layer
All operations grouped into epochs. Double-buffer reality model. Every state transition reconstructable.

### 1.9 Security & Observability
PKU hardware enforcement, cross-domain monitors, full trace via ELF/PKRU/QEMU.

**System Constraints** (final):
- No runtime scheduler
- No dynamic privilege escalation
- No mutable capability graph
